snippet.title: Wangan Midnight R (PS2) Gameplay in 2020
snippet.description:
Before Maximum Tune started, Namco has release Wangan Midnight on February 2, 2001. On December 20, 2001, Wangan Midnight R was released. A PS2 version of Wangan Midnight was released later on March 21, 2002. It was basically a home port of Wangan Midnight R.

I wonder if there's other people know this game exists?
